The tableau worksheet contains a detailed description about all the athletes.

Basketball is a sport which requires energy and quickness in terms of traveling back and forth in the court, and for that the health has to be in a top-notch condition. With the help of age, height and weight, we can figure out who all are in not that good a condition, and if it directly impacts the game (PER). 
If it does, the team needs to rethink about those players.
